parameters: \p3We just got here and... I'm already... sweating...
\knightWho are you, and what's your business here?
\p2You know those four that saved Adon
We're part of the Champion Program
and on the way to Telluria Castle.
\knightYou look the part. Apologies for bothering
you. A big uptick in illegal item smuggling over the
past few months has required groups of guards to
constantly patrol the borders of the Blazing Sands.
\knightI'll make sure you won't be stopped
again. Go now, and make haste to the castle!
I've heard that the king is trying to round up
all the champions as soon as possible.
\knightI have... one more piece of advice for you four.
travelers have reported sensing extreme magical
energy emanating from around the castle.
the royal family is safe, but something
about these reports makes me think there's
a threat we don't know very much about.
